reviews.text:
If I had a whale, I'd name it Oolaa. Because this place must be swimming in the money. Soho prices for standard soho stuff. If you gotta drop a couple hundred for some pasta you've arrived.

Happy hours fair though. And it is family friendly.
Best breakfast ever! Well worth every cent. Staff very friendly.
We love this place! Great for kids and service is good. Coffee is good some days and then its just ok on other days. Good sized food portions too. We are regulars.
Great happy hour prices and the wait staff were just pleasant to talk to. If you need a great atmosphere whether fit work or catching up with friends, this is the place to be.

The vibe was great for a pub but a bit noisy you wanna enjoy a relaxed brunch. Pancakes were average as I found them a bit dry.
But I did enjoy the potato rosti with smoked salmon.

result.formatted_address: Centrestage Tower 1, 108 Hollywood Rd, Sheung Wan, Hong Kong
result.name: Centrestage

reviews.text: Great building to live in
Only cool cats live here.

聚賢居Centrestage，位於港島上環荷李活道108號，於2006年6月落成入伙，算是上環區的「年輕」屋苑，屬於上環去少有的靚住宅屋苑。

由金誠物業Kamson Property 為你提供的資訊，此屋苑由恒基兆業發展。物業共有2座住宅大廈，樓高37層，共有385伙，屋苑主打2至4房單位，面積介乎500至2538方呎不等；全屋苑均以豪宅式包裝，以單位用料高級及華麗會所招徠，特設區內匱乏的恒溫泳池，兼且戶戶有露台，樓價高一線。深受外籍人士及高要求客戶喜愛。租盤及買賣盤一向極其渴市，部分單位更享開揚海景，可預約查詢金誠物業Kamson Property。

而在聚賢居樓下更有數間高質素餐廳、Cafe以及潮流服裝店；周邊附近更有著名的古董街、特色旅遊景點，所以絕對是一個多姿多彩，靜中帶旺的好屋苑！
住戶好撚西
好👌
